ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectSaint Mary's Band Devon I.R. #30 (NB) SETTING APART
PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the SAINT MARY'S BAND, of 446.4 square metres (4805 square feet) of land in the City of Fredericton, New Brunswick, as an addition to Devon Indian Reserve No. 30.
